{% extends "_layouts/base" %}

{% block body %}
    <section class="section">
        <div class="container">
            <h1>
                Field Assistant is a no-bullshit data collection app for researchers.
            </h1>
            <p>
                Key Features:
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li>Offline capable</li>
                <li>Record collection date-time</li>
                <li>Record GPS position</li>
                <li>Attach photos</li>
                <li>Data sets and custom fields</li>
                <li>CSV export (bundled zip)</li>
            </ul>
            <p>
                The app is currently available as a PWA (with a limited feature set) at:
                <br>
                <a href="//bugman-staging.firebaseapp.com/" target="_blank">
                    bugman-staging.firebaseapp.com
                </a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section class="section">
        <div class="container">
            <p>
                The original prototype achieved a great trial run with it's minimum features.
                This expanded into some experimental features for data sets in a beta trial.
            </p>
            <p>
                Although fully capable, the web app environment is restrictive,
                especially on iOS. This led to a native approach using Qt/QML.
                Soon to be released, the full native version features photo support,
                data sets, and bundled zip exports.
            </p>
            <p>
                The original prototype web-app is available
                <a href="//bugman.gwillz.com" target="_blank">here</a>.
                <br>
                The latest web-app is available
                <a href="//bugman-staging.firebaseapp.com" target="_blank">here</a>.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section class="section">
        <div class="container">
            <p>
                <a href="//fieldassistant.app">Field Assistant</a>
            </p>
            <p>
                Gwilyn Saunders + Ben Parslow
                <br>
                Copyright &copy; {{ now|date('Y') }}
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>
